service.name: Approved Program of Work Supplement
service.comment: How is this different from SVC_131?
service.description: Approved Program of Work Supplement (APWS) is a supplementary fortnightly payment available to assist people on eligible income support payments with the costs of participating in an approved program of work.

Dimension.desc: We Fer income support if you are looking for work, completing approved studies or have a disability and are looking for work.
